        },
        "subject": "LU-1866 dt: update interface for dt_index_operations",
        "message": "LU-1866 dt: update interface for dt_index_operations\n\nAlthough it can be implemented indirectly by \"remove + insert\",\nthe direct \"update\" interface is more efficient and semanteme\nclean, and avoid a lot of lock handling for contention.\n\nThe dt_index_operations \"update\" interface is mainly used for\nupdating the record in index file, and for some test purposes.\n\nCurrently, the main user is LFSCK and OI scrub.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I4ca08e8bd6617fcadd63d7803e55ea6e0f9a1ae2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
